#EXDESC
ExDescKey    Sign~
ExDesc       Well, you just learned your first lesson, which is that you can use
look to look at things (just like in real life).  This works with 
signs, objects, people, anything you want to look at - just type LOOK 
<something> or l <something>.
  Another important lesson is how to move from place to place.  You can 
move in 6 possible directions: north, south, east, west, up, and down.  
To move, type the direction you wish to go, or as a shortcut, type the 
first letter.  Test this now by moving east to the next room.
~
#ENDEXDESC

#EXDESC
ExDescKey    marc~
ExDesc       Marc sure is picky! :P
~
#ENDEXDESC

