ExDesc       In order to open the locked door in the next room, you need a key.  
You will find that this little boy is carrying it, and when you loot the 
corpse, you will be carrying the key.  To use a key, type UNLOCK 
<direction>.  You then need to open the door (OPEN <direction>), and then 
you will be able to walk through.  Note that some people are given the 
opportunity to practice a skill called pick lock, which gives you a 
chance of unlocking locked doors without the key.
